author: Chelseahavoc
title: easy to build and rebuild
review:
Over all i really like this set. 
It was a very cute item to get as a freebe at toys'r'us. I like the sticker face but, it doesnt completely match the brick color. I'm a fan of the fire/feather pieces in lego and was happy to get three of them in this set. Just becareful of what direction the wind blows.
